{
  "stem": "7938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As far as we know, we don't know how Madrich people [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Apparently, somebody paid for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know about one family which paid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had money enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they paid for this, and the whole family, four people, went on the list.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it doesn't mean that this was the cause that the people who were in Emalia [? went on ?].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because in Emalia, we didn't have so many people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, certain people from Emalia were liquidated-- were sent out upstairs to-- to the-- to the concentration camp before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, once, an Australian plane fell on the Emalia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the Emalia barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, luckily, it hit the barrack which was emptied few days before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was an [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Australian ?] pilot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was shot down, apparently, by--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came during the night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was shot down by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Gross-Rosen was a camp that I would say there was-- they were-- these were not people anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was people so depressed that they couldn't look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they looked forward, you didn't know-- they were like mannequins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They moved-- when they had to turn their-- their-- their heads to the left or to the right, you could see the whole-- all the-- whole-- the whole-- the whole camp was moving the same way, and nobody looked at you.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody saw you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we came in, we came through-- we came through-- we came through a sauna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to go for showers when we came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They told us to put everything on one place and to go to the showers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, everybody had something with him, and we knew that we wouldn't see this anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was no time to do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
